{"tid":499718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港迪士尼樂園五連加！成人門票明起破$600","createTime":"2017-12-15T06:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T08:11:36.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfced8c4b98092777371ecc6f456a86a55ffd980","tid":499718,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港迪士尼樂園五連加！成人門票明起破$600</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/14/3504761/20171214_news_52_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F3504761%2F20171214_news_52_w.mp4&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=0aca39ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/14/3504761/20171214_news_52_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n繼海洋公園後，另一大型主題公園、香港迪士尼樂園今日亦公佈票價調整，明起標準門票（12至64歲）新售價為港幣$619，小童門票（3至11歲）為港幣$458。兩日標準門票和小童門票分別為港幣$799及港幣$589。長者（65歲或以上）正價門票優惠及合資格殘疾人士享有7折購買1日門票折扣優惠維持不變。長者一日標準門票為港幣$100。今次亦是香港迪士尼連續第五年加價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513239083_8562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513239083_8562.jpg&h=3bcfa1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼表示，港人可享兩個月購票優惠，在明年2月15日前以舊價購買樂園門票，另會同時推出「奇妙處處通」年票會員專享續會特別優惠，及香港居民專享的新入會和門票原價優惠。「奇妙處處通」成人銀卡將調整至港幣$1,238，成人金卡為港幣$1,999，成人白金卡價格則為港幣$3,491。「奇妙處處通」銀卡的售價相等於兩次到訪樂園的門票售價。<br />\n迪士尼發言人補充，加價是因經營成本上升及營運所需。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513242498_1dd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513242498_1dd7.jpg&h=88e379de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171214/57580840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57580840&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=2f7682d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57580840&h=3f56b394\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171214/57580840</a>"},{"pid":"4134ae7cedabfe7bf973c70de9218ca2349adb27","tid":499718,"uid":2455,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"一次都冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe0868a179bff9a2f3949180e36fb5ec1646a65","tid":499718,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"去過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2fc8a30a850c6dd3632369e2433d1c28bc6113","tid":499718,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b2d2efa5ce71b1f30e08df1dd67d7d4bdd86a7","tid":499718,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"你咪加飽佢囉, 反正唔去"},{"pid":"9a8e545dd51800ff29ca4e3061397027c903df94","tid":499718,"uid":111909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"$600去到次短trip啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aa367f317aaa45b222426806df1999d91dcbca","tid":499718,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:09:22.000Z","msg":"話時話上海果個run成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446af483d8423f9a66f8630c5b2f2aef26afa308","tid":499718,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"拆撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"c1d97403e4b8603b984fde8c35be47cd40a41390","tid":499718,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl